  ('2026-04-25', 'enails-consistency-in-dabbing', 'Enails: Consistency in Dabbing', 'An electronic nail (enail) maintains consistent temperature for dabbing, eliminating guesswork with torch heating. They''re pricey but worth it for concentrate connoisseurs.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-04-26', 'spring-picnic-planning', 'Spring Picnic Planning', 'Perfect weather is arriving! Plan a cannabis-friendly picnic with great food, comfortable blankets, and maybe a frisbee. Nature and good company are the best combination.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-04-27', 'cannabis-for-hiv-aids', 'Cannabis for HIV/AIDS', 'Cannabis has been used to combat wasting syndrome, nausea, and pain in HIV/AIDS patients. It''s one of the earliest recognized medical uses, dating back to the 1980s.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-04-28', 'fenchol-the-lavender-cousin', 'Fenchol: The Lavender Cousin', 'Fenchol has a lime, basil, and lavender aroma. It''s being studied for antibacterial properties and may help protect against Alzheimer''s disease by reducing brain inflammation.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-04-29', 'understanding-tolerance-breaks', 'Understanding Tolerance Breaks', 'Regular use builds tolerance. A "T-break" (tolerance break) of even 48 hours can significantly reduce tolerance, making your next session more effective and saving money.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-04-30', 'og-kush-hybrid', 'OG Kush (Hybrid)', 'One of the most famous strains ever, OG Kush is the backbone of West Coast cannabis culture. Its complex aroma and balanced high have made it a timeless favorite.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-01', 'may-day-willie-nelson-s-tribute', 'May Day: Willie Nelson''s Tribute', 'May 1st could be another cannabis holiday! Willie Nelson would approve. Celebrate with his music, support cannabis farmers, and advocate for those still imprisoned for cannabis.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-02', 'grinder-coins-the-kief-trick', 'Grinder Coins: The Kief Trick', 'Drop a clean coin in your grinder''s herb chamber. When you shake it, the coin knocks more trichomes through the screen, collecting more kief faster.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-03', 'may-flowers-session', 'May Flowers Session', '"April showers bring May flowers." Celebrate by buying fresh flowers for your space or visiting a botanical garden. Cannabis enhances appreciation for floral beauty.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-04', 'may-the-fourth-stress-relief', 'May the Fourth: Stress Relief', 'Star Wars Day! Use your favorite strain to manage stress like a Jedi. Cannabis can help you stay calm, focused, and present—even when the Empire strikes back.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-05', 'cinco-de-mayo-celebration', 'Cinco de Mayo Celebration', 'While not terpene-focused, today celebrate cannabis culture''s diversity. Mexican landrace strains like Acapulco Gold have influenced countless modern hybrids.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-06', 'what-is-budtender', 'What is "Budtender"?', 'A budtender is like a sommelier for cannabis. They help you navigate products, suggest strains based on your needs, and educate you about cannabis. Tip them well!
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-07', 'strawberry-banana-indica-dominant', 'Strawberry Banana (Indica-Dominant)', 'This fruity indica crosses Bubble Gum with Banana Kush for a sweet, tropical flavor and deeply relaxing effects. It''s dessert in plant form.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-08', 'david-crosby-the-musical-legend', 'David Crosby: The Musical Legend', 'The legendary musician was open about his cannabis use throughout his career with Crosby, Stills, Nash & Young. His harmonies sound even better enhanced by cannabis.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-09', 'uv-stash-jars-light-protection', 'UV Stash Jars: Light Protection', 'UV light degrades cannabinoids and terpenes. UV-resistant glass jars protect your stash from light damage, preserving potency and flavor longer.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-10', 'mother-s-day-appreciation', 'Mother''s Day Appreciation', 'Whether she partakes or not, appreciate the mother figures in your life. If she does enjoy cannabis, share a special strain or product with her today.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-11', 'cannabis-for-alzheimer-s', 'Cannabis for Alzheimer''s', 'Research suggests cannabinoids may help slow Alzheimer''s progression by reducing inflammation and removing beta-amyloid plaques from the brain. More research is ongoing.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-12', 'cymene-the-cumin-connection', 'Cymene: The Cumin Connection', 'Found in cumin, thyme, and oregano, Cymene has a spicy, earthy aroma. Early research suggests anti-inflammatory and pain-relieving properties.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-13', 'the-history-of-reefer-madness', 'The History of Reefer Madness', 'The 1936 propaganda film "Reefer Madness" portrayed cannabis as causing insanity and violence. Today it''s viewed as a comedy for its outrageous misinformation.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
  ('2026-05-14', 'super-lemon-haze-sativa', 'Super Lemon Haze (Sativa)', 'This two-time Cannabis Cup winner combines Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze for an intensely citrusy, energizing high that''s perfect for creative work.
INSERT INTO day_cards (date, slug, title, body_md, spotlight_json, tags, hero_url) VALUES
