  ('2026-05-25', 'cannabis-for-restless-leg-syndrome', 'Cannabis for Restless Leg Syndrome', 'Many RLS sufferers report relief from cannabis, particularly indica strains before bed. It may reduce the uncomfortable sensations and help improve sleep quality.
